{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":2905,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"身份是依靠邮箱地址hash出来的一串字符串区分的，匿名指的是不能从这串字符串反推出邮箱。删除只是普通用户没权限删，管理员肯定能删啦","timestamp":1592719034,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":2911,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"简单的说系统只知道你是你，这些东西是你发的，但是并不知道你的名字","timestamp":1592719103,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":2959,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: \n1. 嗯，我是想说这句话应该是写错了，没有因果联系。\n2. 这个匿名性很弱，只是相信提供方而已。如果是从哈希推邮箱，因为清华邮件地址较短，穷举一下就出来了，或者可以利用其它系统的漏洞（清华云、开学第一课）获取到的几乎全校同学的邮件地址列表去测试。如果是想要看某人的树洞发言就更简单了，知道对方邮箱算哈希就行。","timestamp":1592719741,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":2973,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 也就是说，这个保密形同虚设?[怕]","timestamp":1592719891,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":2976,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"确实 完全可以允许删除的 不影响匿名性","timestamp":1592719930,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":2988,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 也不尽然，至少需要管理员权限","timestamp":1592720069,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":3023,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 管理员里面无内鬼吧?","timestamp":1592720411,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":3047,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 内鬼可能没有，但可能受到压力变成内鬼","timestamp":1592720633,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":3049,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"例如院系、校方甚至更上级","timestamp":1592720650,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":3183,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"隔壁树洞也有帖子质疑单向加密可靠性。管理员这两天会升级后台系统。","timestamp":1592721510,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":3210,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 所以一般都要加盐的嘛","timestamp":1592721686,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":3342,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 是的，但是这个树洞的设计并没有加盐","timestamp":1592722912,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":3344,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":719,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"而你清邮箱地址可能性非常少，甚至可以直接爆破","timestamp":1592722927,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":719,"reply":13,"tag":null,"text":"小白求教，#118 中说“由于树洞的匿名性，树洞在你发送之后无法删除”，但是洞主在回复树洞的时候会显示为 [洞主]，这不就说明系统是知道操作者是否是洞主吗？那怎么不能删除？","timestamp":1592718756,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782584,"url":"","vote":{}}}